snippet.title: Johnny Depp Says Amber Heard Started Affair With Elon Musk One Month Into Their Marriage!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Says Amber Heard Started Affair With Elon Musk One Month Into Their Marriage!

The drama between Johnny Depp and his fellow actress and ex wife Amber Heard is not even close to ending! In fact, it looks like it has just gotten worse!

Amid reports that the actor has filed a $50 million lawsuit against the actress over her ‘elaborate scheme,’ another detail about their past also emerged.

That being said, Johnny Depp accuses her of having an affair with Elon Musk from the very beginning.

Supposedly, Amber and the Tesla founder started an affair only one month after she had tied the knot with Johnny.

Before now, it was believed that Heard and Musk only dated briefly following her messy divorce from Depp.

The lawsuit, however, states that ‘Unbeknownst to Mr. Depp, no later than one month after his marriage to Ms. Heard, she was spending time in a new relationship with Tesla and Space X founder, Elon Musk.’
